article.headline-text-icon.block-offset-top-and-bottom
  .container-lg
    h1.h2-like.text-center A great organization made even better by great people.
    p.text-center We succeed when our people do. Our benefits support your professional and personal life. That, coupled with our dynamic people have earned us recognition for being a unique and outstanding place to work.
    .awwards
      .awwards__items.js-slider-mobile(
        data-slides-mobile="1"
        data-infinite="true"
        data-arrows="true"
        data-dots="false"
        data-speed="500"
        data-autoplay="false")
        .awwards__item
          .awwards__item__image
            img(src="/images/headline-text-icon-1.png" alt="")
          .awwards__item__textblock.for-mobile
            p For two consecutive years, FORTUNE magazine recognized us as one of the Best Workplaces for Manufacturing &amp; Production for investing in our businesses and people to drive innovation and inspire leadership.
            a(href="/releases/091819_Fortune-Media-Release_FINAL.pdf" target="_blank") Learn More
        .awwards__item
          .awwards__item__image
            img(src="/images/headline-text-icon-2.png" srcset="/images/headline-text-icon-2@2x.png 2x" alt="")
          .awwards__item__textblock.for-mobile
            p For three years in a row, Reynolds American Inc. has been certified as a Great Place to Work for the many ways we are committed to creating an exceptional workplace for our employees.
            a(href="https://www.greatplacetowork.com/certified-company/1000412" target="_blank") Learn More
        .awwards__item
          .awwards__item__image
            img(src="/images/headline-text-icon-3.png" alt="")
          .awwards__item__textblock.for-mobile
            p For the third consecutive year, our internship program was ranked the #1 Best Retail &amp; Consumer Products Internship by Vault.com .
            a(href="https://www.vault.com/internship-program/general-consumer-products/rai-internship-program/internship-opportunities" target="_blank") Learn More
        .awwards__item
          .awwards__item__image
            img(src="/images/headline-text-icon-4.jpg" srcset="/images/headline-text-icon-4@2x.jpg 2x" alt="")
          .awwards__item__textblock.for-mobile
            p Reynolds American Inc. earned a 100% on the Human Rights Campaign’s 2020 Corporate Equality Index, designating us as a Best Place to Work for LGBTQ Equality.
            a(href="/releases/News-Release-RAI-Group-Best-Place-to-Work-for-LGBTQ-Equality-Final-v2.pdf" target="_blank") Learn More

